history.content:
<md>HKN is hosting an info session for Determined AI, an AI startup recently **acquired by Hewlett Packard Enterprise**! This is a great learning experience for those interested in AI, research, and entrepreneurship!
If you’re interested, come to 120B Bechtel on campus on 11/18 (Thursday) at 5 pm! Food provided!  
View event here: [https://fb.me/e/4igCbnssT](https://fb.me/e/4igCbnssT)</md>
history.subject: Learn About Determined AI (AI Startup Recently Acquired by HPE) at this Info Session!
